record.field: for record in self: record[("x_studio_km_per_month")]= record.x_studio_trip_distance_1 * record.x_studio_working_days_per_month* record.x_studio_trips_per_day_1
for record in self: record[("x_studio_km_per_contract")]= record.x_studio_km_per_month * record.x_studio_duration_months
for record in self: record[("x_studio_tons_per_month_1")]= record.x_studio_volume * record.x_studio_working_days_per_month* record.x_studio_trips_per_day_1
for record in self: record[("x_studio_tons_all_trucks")]= record.x_studio_tons_per_contract * record.x_studio_number_of_trucks
for record in self: record[("x_studio_trips_per_month_1")]= record.x_studio_working_days_per_month * record.x_studio_trips_per_day_1
for record in self: record[("x_studio_trips_per_contract")]= record.x_studio_trips_per_month_1 * record.x_studio_duration_months
for record in self: record[("x_studio_monetary_field_CogAo")]= record.x_studio_tons_per_month_1 * record.x_studio_price_per_ton_3
for record in self: record[("x_studio_revenue_all_trucks")]= record.x_studio_revenue_per_contract * record.x_studio_number_of_trucks
